node.text: Love you Conan. Fastest funniest nicest guy of us all. I love you very much my man. And your whole family. From the beginning I looked forward to talking to you on your show and hanging with your gang of greats. Always made it welcoming and fun. And I knew when I couldn't think of anything funny to say out there, you’d think of something for me. To the rescue everytime. A great man and friend for life. Loved watching your show whenever I could and now will love watching you over your fence. Congrats on keeping us all happy this many years. The best. Connnnannnn! Love you pal
